➤ Amazing Facts Media Library - https://www.amazingfacts.org/media-library
➤ Tune into AF Radio - https://www.amazingfacts.org/media-library/listen

Amazing Facts traveled to the Philippines to proclaim the everlasting gospel. Over 10,000 came to hear the messages of hope and truth. Pastor Doug also visited many surrounding areas to spread God's word, from prisons to hospitals around Manila. Hundreds were baptized and many were blessed.
